<div class="row">
	<div class="col-md-4 col-md-offset-1">
		<h2>Where is my Run Dashboard?</h2>
		<p>Since IntelliJ 2017.3 the configuration for activating the Spring Boot Dashboard is somewhat hidden inside the settings:<br>
		Go to "Run/Debug Configurations and look under the "defaults" Tab<br>
			Now there is an additional setting, called "Configurations available inRun Dashboard"<br>
			Here you can add Spring Boot as a Configuration Type
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="col-md-6 col-md-offset-1">
